    "text": "今仔日無啥事體，"
  },
  {
    "type": "pause",
    "duration_ms": 732
  },
  {
    "type": "speech",
    "text": "想著以前讀冊時光，"
  },
  {
    "type": "pause",
    "duration_ms": 979
  },
  {
    "type": "speech",
    "text": "彼個學校名咧，"
  },
  {
    "type": "pause",
    "duration_ms": 1272
  },
  {
    "type": "speech",
    "text": "想袂起來啦，"
  },
  {
    "type": "speech",
    "text": "當時阿母叫伊去菜市仔買餻仔，"
  },
  {
    "type": "speech",
    "text": "毋知買啥物好，"
  },
  {
    "type": "speech",
    "text": "就買些甘蔗同花生，"
  },
  {
    "type": "speech",
    "text": "那個時候佇田裡種稻，"
  },
  {
    "type": "speech",
    "text": "農忙時陣很辛苦，"
  },
  {
    "type": "speech",
    "text": "現在攏老囝囝啦，"
  },
  {
    "type": "speech",
    "text": "轉去休息一下啊。"
